queries.query:
from(bucket: "amibaner-trading")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "stockdata")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Symbol"] == "AAPL")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "CrtPrc" or r["_field"] == "PckPrc" or r["_field"] == "ValPrc" or r["_field"] == "BuyPrc" or r["_field"] == "NoActnLwr" or r["_field"] == "NoActnUpr")
